reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Update: replacement received
reviews.reviewText: UPDATE:First order: I opened it, threw the box away, and plugged it into my car. I smelled electrical burning smells and quicklt unplugged it. The blue LED light worked but nothing more. Since I threw the box away I didnt even think I could send back or get replacement.But I left a review indicating that it was nothing more than a glorified blue light. The company contacted me via email for refund or replacement and even offered to give me an upgraded version. They didnt have to contact me or offer an upgraded replacement. I thanked them and requested the original version/smaller version I previously purchased to be sent to me since I wanted a smaller less bulky item from the start. They sent it to me. The replacement works fine, does what I need it to do and just glad that my first order was just a dud.Important: I recommend this product because of The Company not the product exactly. They stood by their product and offered solutions if things were damaged.

reviews.reviewTitle: INIU USB C Car Charger - Fast and Efficient Charging On the Go
reviews.reviewText: Rating: ★★★★★ (5/5)The INIU USB C Car Charger is a compact and powerful solution for keeping your devices charged while on the road. With a USB C port offering 30W of power and a USB A port providing an additional 30W, this all-metal mini cigarette lighter adapter ensures fast and efficient charging for a wide range of devices, including the latest iPhone models, iPads, Samsung phones, Airpods, and more. Here's why I believe the INIU USB C Car Charger deserves a glowing review:Dual Fast Charging: The combination of a USB C port and a USB A port allows you to charge two devices simultaneously at high speeds.30W Power Output: With a total power output of 30W for each port, this charger is designed to charge your devices quickly and efficiently.Universal Compatibility: This car charger works seamlessly with a variety of devices, making it perfect for families with different devices and needs.Compact and Durable: The all-metal design not only looks sleek but also adds to the charger's durability and heat dissipation.Advanced Safety: Multiple safety features, including protection against overcharging, overheating, and short-circuits, ensure your devices remain safe while charging.In conclusion, the INIU USB C Car Charger is a must-have accessory for those who rely on their devices while traveling. Its dual fast charging, high power output, universal compatibility, compact design, and advanced safety features make it a top-tier choice for on-the-go charging. I can't recommend this car charger enough; it has kept countless individuals' devices charged and ready for action during their travels. Whether you're on a long road trip, commuting to work, or simply running errands, this charger ensures that you never run out of power when you need it most.
